OL,3,CDFDS-Jersey contract to be published
OL,4,Cnext month
OL,6,FA redacted version of the contract
OL,7,Fsigned between the States of Jersey
OL,8,Fand DFDS, the island's new ferry
OL,9,Fprovider, will be published by the end
OL,10,Fof October.
OL,12,FDeputy Kirsten Morel, the Minister
OL,13,Fresponsible for negotiating the ferry
OL,14,Ftender, confirmed the decision to make
OL,15,Fthe contract public in a Economic and
OL,16,FInternational Affairs Scrutiny meeting
OL,17,Fthis afternoon (25 September).
