OL,3,CDFDS-Jersey contract to be published
OL,4,Cnext month
OL,6,FIt comes after increasing levels of
OL,7,Ffrustration from businesses about the
OL,8,Flevel of service being provided by the
OL,9,Foperator - with some going so far as
OL,10,Fto demand the tender is re-negotiated.
OL,12,FThe concession agreement will be
OL,13,Fpartially redacted for legal reasons,
OL,14,Fand commercially sensitive information
OL,15,Fwill not be included.
OL,17,FThe published version will also
OL,18,Fcontain annotated explanations,
OL,19,Fclarifying what some of the clauses
OL,20,Fmean and why they exist.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
