OL,3,CDFDS-Jersey contract to be published
OL,4,Cnext month
OL,6,FThe Department said they believe it's
OL,7,Fnecessary to publish the document
OL,8,Fbecause "every household in the island
OL,9,Fis touched by ferry services", and
OL,10,Fthey wish to provide the public with
OL,11,Fas much transparency as possible on
OL,12,Fwhat has become a relatively
OL,13,Fcontroversial talking point.
OL,15,FRichard Corrigan, the Department's
OL,16,FChief Officer, added, "The contract is
OL,17,Ffar more comprehensive than the
OL,18,Foutgoing operating agreement, which
OL,19,Ffrom Jersey's standpoint was a really
OL,20,Fpoor agreement.
