OL,3,CDFDS-Jersey contract to be published
OL,4,Cnext month
OL,6,F"We believe we have a contract that is
OL,7,Fcommercially appropriate and
OL,8,Funderwrites resilient services well
OL,9,Finto the future.
OL,11,F"It secures significant investment in
OL,12,Fthe passenger experience and resilient
OL,13,Ffreight supply to the island."
OL,15,FThe scrutiny panel also asked the
OL,16,FDepartment about concerns from
OL,17,Fbusinesses on "hidden" additional
OL,18,Ffreight costs.
