OL,6,F"They were previously absorbed by
OL,7,FCondor within their freight rate", Mr
OL,8,FCorrigan adds, but DFDS have chosen
OL,9,Fnot to do this.
OL,11,FHowever, Mr Corrigan added the
OL,12,FDepartment doesn't believe "any
OL,13,Fcharges should come as a surprise",
OL,14,Fand the company has conceded to absorb
OL,15,Fthe charges up to 31 July.
OL,17,FThe Department is currently
OL,18,Fnegotiating whether "some other
OL,19,Fmechanism might be applied" to
OL,20,Fmitigate costs until the end of the
OL,21,Fyear.
